data.description: Make this your first and last stop! This 2000+ square foot all brick cape cod is boasting with space. Walk through the foyer,  into an amazing open floor plan to the living room with fireplace and expansive dining room. ALL new SS appliances,  cabinets and granite counter tops. New carpet throughout. Fresh paint throughout. W/D on main floor as well as Primary  Bedroom with fireplace, Large walk-in closet and fully updated ensuite bathroom with granite. Two bedrooms upstairs and  Large fullY updated bathroom. New roof 2018 with warranty. Newer windows, Convenient to Shopping, NSU, 264, Ghent and Downtown Norfolk. W/D & Security system convey. This house has tons of character, fully updated and is TURN KEY! $5k Homebuyer grant or $2k VA loan closing cost grant with use of preferred lender available.
